---
title: Easy Peasy Korean Style Beef Noodles with Stir-Fried Veg
description: Super speedy, these Easy Peasy Korean Style Beef Noodles take only 15 minutes to make. The popular Korean condiment gochujang contains chillies, fermented soybeans and glutinous rice which give it its savoury-sweet flavour.
